******
[1] Guinea: transmission at funerals
Date: Fri 15 May 2015
Source: Reuters [edited]
http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/05/15/us-health-ebola-guinea-idUSKBN0O01M220150515


Guinea Ebola cases climb due to transmissions at funerals
---------------------------------------------------------
[According to figures released on Tuesday [12 May 2015] by the special government department set up to fight the disease, treatment clinics were handling just 8 confirmed Ebola cases. According to Fode Tass Sylla, special government department spokesperson: "Today we have 27 sick in our treatment centers, including 18 confirmed cases. Yesterday alone we recorded 5 sick." He also said all the new patients had contracted Ebola virus disease at funeral ceremonies.]

