Italy: Emergency nurse with Ebola 'stable,' 10 under watch
----------------------------------------------------------
[3 people (the nurse's mother and 2 sisters) are under quarantine, and 10 people on the island of Sardinia are being monitored by health authorities for signs of Ebola virus disease.]

